dowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Fufufu, that's definitely true.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"The fact that Poppin'Party can do that when the time calls is amazing. That's what I mean by initiative.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"I don't know if I believe it myself, but... it does make me happy to know people around me see us like that.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"We do! Remember that time with the downtown festival? You guys were running all over the place, weren't you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"You were really amazing back then! All of us in Afterglow were talking about you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Tomoe and Tsugu were so happy that the festival was actually happening.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Ah. Now that you mention it, Tomoe-chan did say that when we had that concert together at CiRCLE.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"It felt good to know that we made her happy.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"There's no way Afterglow would be able to do anything like that.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Really? I don't think it was anything special...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Oh, yeah! Maybe Afterglow should get in on that whole toy collection thing, too!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"If we set up a box at Haneoka, I'm sure we'll be able to collect a bunch!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Maybe Poppin'Party's rubbing off on me, too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"I think that's a great idea! Kasumi-chan would be so happy!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"You think? Then I guess I can't disappoint her♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Yeah. To think our little idea would spread all the way over to Haneoka... This is incredible.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"It might not stop at Haneoka, you know. This might get bigger and bigger from here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Really? That'd be so great if it did...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Hey, so how did all this start in the first place? C'mon, tell me!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"ev102-ep2-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"Rimi","body":"Of course!","tenti